Fleq FAQs - Fleq The Alliance How It Works FAQs Press Register < BACK TO HOME Frequently Asked Questions The Basics What is Fleq? Fleq is the combination of the words “flexible” and “equity” and we’re changing the way you think about What is the Fleq Alliance? The Fleq Alliance is a new way to buy a The Alliance uses a partnership approach to purchase a home of your There is no debt or mortgage when you use an Alliance to buy your Where is the Fleq Alliance available? Fleq will be rolling out the Alliance in limited markets in and will be expanding Check back soon for updates or to receive Forming An Alliance Are there any limitations when I am searching for a home? There are no specific limitations when choosing your home other than it must be in Homes with unique features or marketability issues may not qualify or require a larger initial equity What happens if I want to back out of an Alliance? At any time before the partnership purchases your home, you can back out of an There are no penalties, but a prospective Member will have been required to pay for certain costs associated with creating an Depending on when a prospective Member backs out, some or all of these costs may not be How is my initial equity contribution determined? Fleq considers many factors before determining a Member s required initial equity These factors include, but are not limited to, your credit history, current income to projected rent and the cost of the home to be Is there a minimum credit score required to become a Member? There is no minimum credit score and credit score is only one of a number of factors (including but not limited to prior rental history, criminal background check, rent to monthly income ratio, etc) that Fleq reviews before forming an Alliance with a potential How long does an Alliance last? An Alliance has no set time Although the lease will have finite duration, it contains automatic renewal provisions, which could extend for as long as the Member wishes it to do So as long as the Member has not sold the home, provided notice to Fleq that they wish to terminate the lease, or are in default under the lease or the operating agreement, an Alliance can last Member Fundamentals What is included in my monthly payment? Your monthly payment includes amounts for rent and for normal ownership Rent is paid only for the portion of the home you don t Conversely, you only pay ownership expenses on the part of the home you do How does the cost of equity change over time? Each year the partnership s home will be valued by The value of the home divided by the number of partnership equity units will create the purchase price for the This price is then locked in for the next Is there a limit to the amount of equity that can be purchased? A Member can purchase as little or as much equity as they want (up to %) at any time or over any period of When can I purchase additional equity? A Member can purchase equity whenever they want Do changes in interest rates affect my monthly payments? There is no debt in an Alliance so changes in interest rates do not impact your monthly Do I have to pay a security deposit? No! As a result of you being a member of the ownership group and a tenant, Fleq does not require you to pay additional cash to guarantee that you will not damage your Ending An Alliance Do I have the right to sell the partnership’s home? The Inhabiting Member retains the right to sell the What if I have to move? In addition to having the option to sell the home, if the Member wants to start a new Alliance on a new home, you can transfer the equity in your current home to your new Fleq will take back your current property eliminating the pain and hassle of needing to sell a Do I have to consult with Fleq before selling the partnership’s home? You do not have to consult with Fleq before selling the However, Fleq has a right of first refusal on any agreed upon sales If a Member consults with Fleq prior to the sale, Fleq may waive its right of first refusal as long as the sale price is above an agreed upon floor What happens if I can’t make the required payments? If a Member fails to pay rent, the Member may be evicted under the terms of their If a Member fails to pay for their share of ownership costs, Fleq will seek remedies to cover those costs under the partnership s Operating What happens to my equity if I default on the lease? Even if you are evicted due to a default on the lease, a Member retains their ownership interests subject to offsets for any legal costs incurred by Additional Questions Does FLEQ have decision making power without my consent? Fleq is the managing member of the As such, Fleq is in charge of various administrative affairs of the Alliance as well as setting the value of the equity and setting market rents for future As long as a Member is current under the lease, Fleq can never sell the property or cancel the Who pays for the cost of home improvements? The Inhabiting Member pays for the cost of home

About Candle | Candle Homepage Candle Home About Candle The Team Blog Our Mission At Candle, our mission is to democratize To do that we need to close the gap between what you can easily build today and where modern expectations are for This gap is filled with hard work that results in zero differentiable Tasks like integration and boilerplate, work like authentication, storage, and It s the cost of playing the Modern software leaders found success when this gap was narrow, when the cost of entry was The gap widened as the industry Companies simply had to do Companies that form today have an list of requirements while established companies keep pulling further into the Today, it s difficult to compete without spending millions of dollars only to get to a competitive There are indeed shortcuts, but they come at a SaaS products and cloud platforms get you far quickly, but you tie your company to a monthly bill that never stops It s not a healthy way to grow a sustainable Democratizing software means leveling the playing It means making building, running, maintaining, testing, securing and scaling software cheaper and It means giving you speed and adaptability without To us, it means a more promising future for our friends and How are we going to do it? To level any playing field, you need to build up low areas or tear down higher At Candle, we re tackling both Code is cheap, but integration is Managing millions of lines of integration code is a weak competitive advantage, so we re ironing out the wrinkles that prevent code from integrating When everything has the same interface, code naturally connects to other code like a Functionality is easier to add, change, and Dependencies are easier to update and Testing is so straightforward that it bares no resemblance to what we do Wasmflow captures these connections into components and flows that define complete pieces of Components are open and composable so you can take any component, alter the flow, and make it your The Wasmflow runtime is free and You can run Wasmflow applications We are building this foundation to do fundamentally new things with We have exciting ideas in store that will change how you think of building and running Commoditization and automation changes At Candle, we re commoditizing logic and automating dozens of tasks traditionally left to senior When we re done, companies built on mountains of bespoke source code will no longer find themselves so far ©2022 Candle   Candle Homepage Candle Home About Candle The Team Blog Making software development faster, more secure, and less Do more with ©2022 Candle

Support Our Mission About Us The History of Maristans Perhaps one of the most unique manifestations of Islamic Civilization are the Maristans , or institutions of healing, that boasted the world’s first treatment centers for treating psychological Given the holistic framing of the Islamic worldview, it was no accident that these healing centers embedded the treatment of psychological illnesses into their In so doing, Maristans became a trademark of the Muslim world and could be found in major metropolitan cities from the Century These healing institutions forever changed the understanding and treatment of psychological illnesses by first dedicating specialized wards for psychological illnesses within the larger Islamic hospital complex, later followed by institutions solely dedicated to the treatment of the mentally Maristans & Islamic Psychology It is imperative to note that the creation of the very first healing institutions dedicated to treating psychological illnesses is unique to the Muslim world as it was inspired directly by Islamic teachings found in the Qu’ran and the Sunnah of the Prophet Most importantly, the interdisciplinary nature of these healing centers mirrored the interdisciplinary nature of the emerging field we today refer to as Islamic In short, the Maristans served as the center where theoretical concepts developed by early Muslim physicians, theologians, and who contributed to the creation of Islamic Psychology, were translated into practical, clinical Many of the novel methods, tools, and approaches for treating psychological illnesses developed in the Maristans of the Muslim world can be utilized today in formulating a practical implementation of Islamic Historical sources reveal that Maristans spread in the Muslim lands between and centuries were known to provide treatment for psychological conditions through a holistic understanding of health and illness utilizing a wide range of Environmental and personal factors were considered in a broader perspective for diagnosis and treatment so that the of body, mind, and soul could be holistically A variety of treatment methods including medication, music therapy, water sounds, baths, healthy balanced diet, cupping, and talk therapy were offered by a multidisciplinary team who cared for the Furthermore, the physical features of Maristans such as their location, architectural design, and landscape were an instrumental part of the psychological healing Maristan Today Our online clinical, educational, and Maristan initiative was inspired by the historical function of traditional Our goal is to revive the Islamic traditional function of Maristans with research and education, stemming from the work of the Stanford Muslim Mental Health & Islamic Psychology Lab, to inform holistic healing for our clients and provide culturally and spiritually congruent, professional, accessible, affordable mental health care for Maristan Zacate Ave, Fremont CA Our Carbon Budget works towards the goal of keeping our planet’s temperature from rising more than °C—in line with targets set by the UN Environmental Programme (UNEP) . In order to achieve this, we need to reduce our annual greenhouse gas (GHG) emissions from gigatons of carbon dioxide equivalent (GtCO₂e)—an estimate for what we emitted in —to GtCO₂e by the year That’s a % reduction of our collective emissions, and we have ten years to get Working its way back from this objective, the Carbon Budget sets out yearly, global carbon emissions The Carbon Budget for the year is This is our collective carbon emissions budget for the entire You can contribute to this goal as a #GlobalCitizen by monitoring your Daily Carbon Check out Carbon Lingo for more! What are Carbon Statements? Simply put, our Carbon Statements are streamlined reports on the carbon footprint of consumer They look a lot like Nutrition Facts labels—how are Carbon Statements different? While Nutrition Facts labels report on nutritional components of food items and their pertinence to your body, our Carbon Statements report on the carbon emissions associated with products and their pertinence to the Instead of relating information in the context of a recommended daily amount as Nutrition Facts labels do, we relate ours in the context of a recommended daily quota—derived from the Carbon Hence the term Carbon Statement . While Nutrition Facts labels address facts, which are fixed, our Carbon Statements (like bank statements) account for facts and This is an important distinction because our choices and actions over the lifespan of a product increase or decrease the cumulative carbon emissions associated with said This is why we prepare multiple Carbon Statements for the same The Statements will differ, for example, based on whether the consumer chooses to the , or whether the producer chooses to transport the to its point of sale using a vehicle powered by fossil fuels renewable WHAT IS C02e? This is shorthand for “carbon dioxide ” Carbon dioxide (CO₂) overwhelmingly accounts for most greenhouse gas (GHG) Since CO₂ is the most prevalent, other GHGs are converted into the common unit CO₂e using conversion factors based on their global warming potential (GWP) relative to For example, one metric ton of Methane (CH₄) has around the same GWP as thirty metric tons of carbon dioxide (CO₂), and is therefore represented as This is similar to converting monetary amounts of different currencies into a single base currency in order to compare Check out Carbon Lingo for more! FAQ - Reseller Features FAQ s Brand FAQ s Reseller FAQ s About Us Contact Sign Up Brand Sign Up Reseller Sign Up Log In BRAND FAQS Standard Basic Privacy Security Payment Ordering B2B Tax Compliance Integrations Standard Basic What is MidwayPlus? MidwayPlus is a buying solution that positions your shop’s sales and service abilities in front of the Brands you buy every When you partner with MidwayPlus, you have the opportunity to showcase your buying How much is MidwayPlus for a reseller? MidwayPlus is a free solution for qualified and verified How do we join as a reseller? Visit and click on Reseller Sign It is important that this platform is for wholesale transactions within the automotive industry by businesses with a stake in the industry, so we will ask some qualifying questions and verify the Can a reseller also be a brand? The only company that can sell a particular Brand is the Brand itself but we recognize that there are some companies that are both a Brand and a We welcome these At the present time, this scenario will require two different accounts within How long does it take to be approved as a reseller? It typically takes business days to be approved as a Are we buying from MidwayPlus or the Brand? You are buying from the MidwayPlus facilitates easy shopping and order management for you and easy product listings and order management for the Brands, but your purchase and payment are directly with the Privacy Security Can we see other resellers information? MidwayPlus will never share Reseller information with other Brands will be able to see the profile a Reseller creates for the site and certain attributes of a Reseller, such as type of business, specialty, This benefits the Reseller by allowing Brands to target Resellers with special Does MidwayPlus share purchase history, our or customer information with anyone? MidwayPlus uses industry leading payment processing companies to store credit card information securely and to process Payment What are the payment options? You may pay with any standard credit card: Visa, Mastercard, or American We also have a trade credit facility called Shop Lender, offer the ability for Brands to offer Net Terms, and will soon offer the ability to pay via Does the payment go directly to the Brand? Your payment is remitted directly to the The Brand’s remittance advice shows your name, as it appears on your credit Ordering Can we purchase from any brand that is using MidwayPlus? Each Brand controls which Resellers they sell Because MidwayPlus verifies that Resellers are legitimate businesses with a stake in the automotive aftermarket industry, some Brands will choose to make their products for sale to all Resellers on the However, there are many Brands on the platform that have not yet authorized you to buy from MidwayPlus makes it easy for you to request to buy from a Are we direct with every brand available on MidwayPlus? Yes and no! If a Brand allows a purchase, you are However, some Brands require for initial MidwayPlus makes it easy to apply using guided workflows, messaging, and communication Can we purchase multiple Brands on one order (PO)? Yes! We will break a PO into sections and only send each Brand a PO for their products, but you will be able to place one PO and manage it as one order within your MidwayPlus Order Management Can you integrate into my systems to make ordering easier for me? Using our APIs are EDI and ERP or other system integrations are available for a small Contact is for more information about any integration you have in mind! B2B Tax Compliance Do we need to upload our tax documents with each brand? You only need to upload your tax documents one time to Our platform will track the states for which you have a Reseller exemption certificate and make sure you are not charged sales tax for those states, regardless of which Brands you are purchasing Payments Why would we pay tax on an order if its B2B? As more business has moved online, States have adapted to make sure they are capturing all sales tax on retail If you have a Reseller exemption certificate for a state you are shipping to, you will not need to pay sales If you see sales tax applied to your order, it is because we do not have an exemption certificate for you on file for the Do you remind us when a certificate is going to expire? We do! We recognize that managing tax exemptions in multiple states is an administrative chore and will do everything we can to help you keep those certificates up to date in our Integrations Can MidwayPlus integrate into our QuickBooks software? We have several integrations to popular ERP and Accounting packages, such as QuickBooks and Check with us to learn what is If we do not yet have an integration to your preferred system, we’d be happy to discuss creating one for Can we get a Brands data inventory feed? Yes! You can receive a data feed from all Brands that have approved you for API access is made available according to similar Features Contact T

We re working hard to make it a more open and inclusive space, beginning with model Our first event turned out to be a major success, which showed the true extent of our reach, and can provide an opportunity for your name to stand out among the elite group of people and companies supporting our Contact Us CURRENT HOT NOZZLE SPONSORS © Hot Nozzle Society   Event | Hot Nozzle Society Home Event Location Booster s Club Event FAQ HPR Guide Sponsor Team Shop Hot Nozzle Summer What originally began as a joke quickly gained traction on the digital supernova of Twitter and led to the creation of the first ever “Hot Nozzle Summer” Amateur rocketeers from different backgrounds and experience levels gathered together in the desert with the common goal of launching rockets and having From this emerged the idea of creating an established organization with the goal of creating a space in which rocketry can be accessible to © Hot Nozzle Society   Home | Hot Nozzle Society Home HNS Event FAQ Sponsor Team HPR Guide Contact TO L1 & BEYOND HOT NOZZLE SUMMER READ MORE HNS LORE Hot Nozzle Society (HNS - formerly Hot Nozzle Summer) is a movement within the amateur rocketry community that seeks to break down the barriers that exist within the hobby, in order to make rocketry more accessible to new people, regardless of their rocketry or engineering skill HNS celebrates all aspects of amateur rocketry, whether it s getting an official certification through NAR or Tripoli, or just shooting model rockets in the backyard with your kids this HNS was born in a digital supernova on Twitter - beginning as a joke, but quickly spreading like wildfire For the history on how this began, you can check out this Twitter thread THE HOT NOZZLE MISSION Hot Nozzle Society seeks to create a welcoming and vibrant environment for those looking to enter or expand their knowledge of rocketry, regardless of age, race, gender, status, and Outreach Providing resources for all to learn the wonders of rocketry Experience An inclusive event for those looking for mentorship and experience Community A welcoming and vibrant community for support within the hobby © Hot Nozzle Society   FAQ | Hot Nozzle Society Home Event Location Booster s Club Event FAQ HPR Guide Sponsor Team Shop FAQ If our FAQ doesn t answer your question, feel free to contact us below Contact © Hot Nozzle Society
